### ðŸ§° Troubleshooting by Layer

| Layer | Tool                     | What It Helps Diagnose           |
|-------|--------------------------|----------------------------------|
| 1     | `ping`, cable tester     | Connection, physical issues      |
| 2     | `ipconfig`, `ifconfig`   | MAC, interface errors            |
| 3     | `tracert`, `ping`        | Routing problems                 |
| 4     | Port scanner             | TCP/UDP blocked or filtered      |
| 7     | Browser DevTools         | Web-based issues                 |

